            "id": "693b428b9710780001fe39ed",
            "title": "RH Stock Soars After Mixed Q3 Earnings",
            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-jSieiP ipaQzy\"><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>RH </strong><a class=\"ticker-link\" data-exchange=\"NYSE\" data-ticker=\"NX\" href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/quote/NX\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">(NYSE:</a><a class=\"ticker\" href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/quote/RH\" target=\"_blank\">RH</a>)<!-- --> shares climbed in Thursday's extended trading after the company released a mixed third-quarter earnings report.  </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Here's a look at the details from the quarter. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>RH stock is moving. Watch the price action here.</strong></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>The Details: </strong>RH reported quarterly earnings of $1.71 per share, which missed the analyst estimate of $2.16 by 20.87%, according to data from <a href=\"https://pro.benzinga.com/?gspk=YWRhbWVja2VydDUzMzY&amp;gsxid=zBMR4PKmcgBw\" target=\"_blank\">Benzinga Pro</a>.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Quarterly revenue came in at $883.81 million, which beat the Street estimate of $883.69 million.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">“We continued to generate industry-leading growth with revenue increasing 9% in the third quarter, and up 18% on a two-year basis, demonstrating the disruptive nature of our brand despite the worst housing market in almost 50 years and the polarizing impact of tariffs,” CEO <strong>Gary Friedman</strong> said in a <a href=\"https://d1io3yog0oux5.cloudfront.net/_7ec15d93692ae2bc1d8de6064cbeff24/rh/db/3613/33682/shareholder_letter/RH+Q3+2025+Financial+Results+and+Shareholder+Letter.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">letter to shareholders</a>.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Outlook: </strong>RH sees fourth-quarter revenue in a range of $869.27 million to $877.4 million, versus the $896.97 million analyst estimate.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>RH Stock Price:</strong> According to data from<a href=\"https://pro.benzinga.com/?gspk=YWRhbWVja2VydDUzMzY&amp;gsxid=zBMR4PKmcgBw\" target=\"_blank\"> Benzinga Pro</a>, RH stock was up 9.58% to $168 in Thursday's extended trading.  </p><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/markets/tech/25/12/49317474/space-stocks-2025-year-in-review-rocket-lab-executes-spacex-ipo-ahead\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Space Stocks 2025 Year In Review: Rocket Lab Executes, SpaceX IPO Ahead?</strong></a><strong> </strong></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><em>Photo: Shutterstock</em></p><!--/$--><!--$--><div><div><div class=\"bz-optimizely-campaign bz-optimizely-campaign-middle-49350782\" data-nosnippet=\"true\"></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></div>",
